description:
GrapeCity Spread WinForms (GcSpread) is a cross-platform library that allows to create, analyze, and modify XLSX documents.

Its object model closely follows the Excel and models the Visual Studio Tools for Office APIs.

In addition, GrapeCity Spread WinForms includes a powerful calculation engine and other high-level features that make XLSX document creation easy and convenient.

The online GrapeCity Spread WinForms sample browser is available at https://www.grapecity.com/spreadnet#demos
title: GrapeCity Spread WinForms for .NET Standard 2.0
